dct_description_sm: AMS (FEC) In upper left margin: Korea city plans 1:10,000. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals with 10 meter supplementary contours, and spot elevations. Place names transcribed according to the McCune-Reischauer System. Compiled by photogrammetric methods from aerial photography and by reference to Cn'unch'on 1:10,000 Japanese Imperial Land Survey, 1934. Map is not field checked.
